{"MARY-BUD":[{"def":"The marigold; a blossom of the marigold.","pos":""}],"MARYSOLE":[{"def":"A large British fluke, or flounder (Rhombus megastoma); -- called also carter, and whiff.","pos":""},{"def":"Native sulphate of ammonia, found in volcanic districts; -- so named from Mascagni, who discovered it.","pos":""}]}